{"tid":352921,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKU HALL] 各hall hall pub大比拼","createTime":"2017-08-09T07:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T04:40:59.000Z","uid":134458,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95e286a6b0ef0ab0902b7b8404e2551199cbc090","tid":352921,"uid":134458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"又到reg day各hall都會出唔同既hall pub<br />\n因為我都係整pub既人所以都幾鍾意睇下其他hall d pub咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋hall pub某程度上都睇得出間hall係點（間hall對收fm重唔重視，有冇心搞）<br />\n真心hall pub柒既唔會有fm想入啦<br />\n下列係唔同hall既hall page，fm可以入去睇下，因為youtube channel唔會有齊d pub，想了解清楚既就去hall page睇啦<br />\n<br />\nhysan：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LeeHysanHallHKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLeeHysanHallHKU%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=57437629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LeeHysanHallHKU/</a><br />\n哩個真係要屌 個reg day video又悶又重覆 完全冇skills可言 小學生都整到啦<br />\nd 音樂又唔知做咩咁 個flow又唔知想點 完全唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsuen chi sun：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SuenChiSunHall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSuenChiSunHall%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=feab6bb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SuenChiSunHall/</a><br />\n哩個真係估佢唔到，今年scs publication方面突然極之認真同博盡<br />\n留意左佢幾年 d video既質素不嬲都算唔錯 但今年突然整左極多唔同種類既video同post<br />\n例如扮新假期既系列 最新果段訪問 大家自己上hall page睇<br />\n雖然係對手但係pub層面上真係比個叻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nstarr：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/starrhallhku/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstarrhallhku%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e678a491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/starrhallhku/</a><br />\n個plot每年間間其實都差唔多 冇新意 但保持到一貫既水準<br />\n係mtr跳舞幾新鮮 hall page入面有唔同既文章 文青路線<br />\n<br />\nstjohns：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stjohns.hk/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstjohns.hk%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=51521375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stjohns.hk/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n個reg day介紹得幾詳盡 係幾幫到fm手既 都比個叻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nrc lee：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkurcleehall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkurcleehall%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=764676a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkurcleehall/</a><br />\n都係果d年年一樣既plot 不過起碼整得好過hysan先<br />\n都出多左d新題型既videos 有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nweilun：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkurcleehall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkurcleehall%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=764676a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkurcleehall/</a><br />\n勁早就出左reg day video，抵讚<br />\n而且題材有新意 唔再係間間年年都一樣既plot<br />\nnice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlee shau kee：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkulskh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkulskh%2F&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=77ac00f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkulskh/</a><br />\n有心機 有新意 第一人視角<br />\n睇得出整video既人功力極深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他hall本人認為冇咩野好講 ricci哩d想入就會入唔會睇pub <br />\nd 柒既hall都係冇得揀而揀所以都唔會睇pub<br />\nsuggest fm揀之前去fb page，youtube channel睇多d<br />\n之前幾年既video都可以睇<br />\n一方面可以了解多d 睇下d人<br />\n另一方面我哩d pub撚認為一間hall既pub其實可以睇得出間hall既心機 心意<br />\n希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n估唔估到邊間既係我整haha</span>"},{"pid":"bdc45176cceb99e9c251e54d97f5d70c3e98eccc","tid":352921,"uid":64779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8445dd24d6495e1fc26b0b0f8d33e8efc96b935e","tid":352921,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"Freshmen 你地好呀 我地係HKU St. John's College<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎Reg Day係咪仲考慮緊住邊間Hall呢<br />\n過黎報我地既FNS 2017 Momentos Eternos 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDate: 12 - 13 August 2017<br />\nTime: 12:45 - 23:00 next day<br />\nVenue: St. John's College, 82 Pokfulam Road<br />\nCamp Fee: HKD 300<br />\nEligibility: Freshmen of HKU<br />\n報名Link: <a href=\"http://goo.gl/aMM3cp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FaMM3cp&d=eO2QlBbbCN36DLD6Qb5d58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a901c406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/aMM3cp</a><br />\n<br />\n有啲咩問題都可以隨時問我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://d1k5w7mbrh6vq5.cloudfront.net/images/cache/3c/59/12/3c5912411ab3136ef2f34b2517df68f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fd1k5w7mbrh6vq5.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2Fcache%2F3c%2F59%2F12%2F3c5912411ab3136ef2f34b2517df68f2.jpg&h=e428bc4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3353faed4d98706f04e60bf959f4e310a7b20d27","tid":352921,"uid":134458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Freshmen 你地好呀 我地係HKU St. John's College<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎Reg Day係咪仲考慮緊住邊間Hall呢<br />\n過黎報